            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>易用友好的高性能监控告警系统。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dromara/hertzbeat@gh-pages/img/badge/web-monitor.svg" alt="tan-cloud"/>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dromara/hertzbeat@gh-pages/img/badge/ping-connect.svg" alt="tan-cloud"/>
